OOC: Recon couldnt possibly be on the ship, no matter what.

BIC:
Sinnertwin lands on top of Blot from the impact of the crashing. "Blot get
off of us" one of the heads yells, as anothers jaws snap at Blot.

Meanwhile, the small creature that was hiding in the shadows slinks out,
following Hung-grr, "Dont be so rash Hung-grr. How do you know these
Decepticons will be on your side?".
